logs.message:
Version conflict detected for Xamarin.Android.Support.Compat. Install/reference Xamarin.Android.Support.Compat 28.0.0.3 directly to project Camera.Android to resolve this issue. 
 Camera.Android -> Camera -> Xamarin.Essentials 1.3.1 -> Xamarin.Android.Support.Compat (>= 28.0.0.3) 
 Camera.Android -> Xamarin.Android.Support.Design 27.0.2.1 -> Xamarin.Android.Support.Compat (= 27.0.2.1).
